\f2\b0\fs21 \cf16 \cb30 \strokec16 When Nekomata's 
\f0\b \cf17 \strokec17 Dodge Counter
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  or 
\f0\b \cf17 \strokec17 Quick Assist
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  hits an enemy, her DMG increases by 
\f0\b \cf31 \strokec31 60%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  for 40s. Repeated triggers reset the duration.\cb1 \
\cb30 Nekomata gains 40 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zzz.nanoka.cc/character/1021#ZzzTerm1000024"}}{\fldrslt \ul Purr Energy}} upon entering the battlefield. In Investigation Zone mode, this effect can trigger once every 180s.\cb1 \
\cb30 While Nekomata is in-combat, she gains 1 [Purr Energy] every second, up to a maximum of 60. Different skills restore different amounts of [Purr Energy] when they hit an enemy.\cb1 \
\cb30 When Nekomata has at least 40 [Purr Energy] and after triggering a 
\f0\b \cf17 \strokec17 Perfect Dodge
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , press \cb1 \dn3 {{\NeXTGraphic Icon_Evade.webp \width960 \height960 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}洞\cb30 \up0  to consume 30 [Purr Energy] and activate [Dodge: Disappearing Tail]. Then press \cb1 \dn3 {{\NeXTGraphic Icon_Normal.webp \width960 \height960 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}洞\cb30 \up0  to perform [Dodge Counter: Fluffy Piercing Claw] once without consuming [Purr Energy].\cb1 \
\cb30 When Nekomata has at least 40 [Purr Energy], hold \cb1 \dn3 {{\NeXTGraphic Icon_Normal.webp \width960 \height960 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}洞\cb30 \up0  to consume 40 [Purr Energy] and activate [Dodge Counter: Fluffy Piercing Claw].\cb1 \
\cb30 Using [Dodge Counter: Fluffy Piercing Claw] grants {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zzz.nanoka.cc/character/1021#ZzzTerm1000025"}}{\fldrslt \ul Pawpad Ambush}} state for 40s. Repeated triggers reset the duration. While [Pawpad Ambush] is active, all of Nekomata's attacks that hit are treated as hitting enemies from behind.\cb1 \
\cb30 While [Pawpad Ambush] is active, Nekomata's attacks that hit trigger [Super Mean Pawprint], dealing an additional instance of 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Physical DMG
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  equal to 30% of her ATK. This effect can trigger once every 1s.\cb1 \
\cb30 Nekomata restores 20 additional [Purr Energy] when using her Ultimate, 10 when using her Chain Attack, and 5 when using her EX Special Attack.\cb1 \
